有没有一些好的安全防范类的产品推荐，或者有没有去过的分享些安全经验啥的？</p>\n","last_modified":1689558935,"replies":21,"id":957282},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1689070442","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1689070442","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":57351,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1689070442","stars":8482,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":530773,"username":"TESTFLIGHT2021","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/TESTFLIGHT2021","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f81d1103c117a67a0be5f6f3081250bc?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f81d1103c117a67a0be5f6f3081250bc?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f81d1103c117a67a0be5f6f3081250bc?s=73&d=retro","created":1611753956,"last_modified":1611753956},"last_reply_by":"TESTFLIGHT2021","last_touched":1689566214,"title":"想做个公司网站，需求如下，能找到兼职人员么？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/957326","created":1689562873,"deleted":0,"content":"1.公司网站以出售商品为主，能做到商品分类展示，商品详情页面能自己编辑，插入图片，插入表格，插入文件下载；\r\n2.最好是团队，前端+后端+美工；\r\n3.代码简洁，安全性好，可以用开源框架，需要提供代码，如果合作愉快，可以长期付费维护；\r\n4.数据库 Mysql 或者 PGsql ；\r\n5.网站设计时候考虑多语言特性，产品针对很多语言地区市场。","content_rendered":"<p>1.公司网站以出售商品为主，能做到商品分类展示，商品详情页面能自己编辑，插入图片，插入表格，插入文件下载；\n2.最好是团队，前端+后端+美工；\n3.代码简洁，安全性好，可以用开源框架，需要提供代码，如果合作愉快，可以长期付费维护；\n4.数据库 Mysql 或者 PGsql ；\n5.网站设计时候考虑多语言特性，产品针对很多语言地区市场。</p>\n","last_modified":1689562873,"replies":18,"id":957326},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1689070442","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1689070442","title":"程序员","url":"https