ull,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5141c0f3d760d1e5d9515c0944bc120c?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5141c0f3d760d1e5d9515c0944bc120c?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5141c0f3d760d1e5d9515c0944bc120c?s=73&d=retro","created":1523867925,"last_modified":1689553691},"last_reply_by":"littlefishcc","last_touched":1689558136,"title":"真没见过这种问题，求帮助","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/957240","created":1689553759,"deleted":0,"content":"前提：公司有两台转发服务器，一台 nginx ，一个 IIS 服务，有一个用户信息图片上传接口，已经稳定运行 2 年。\r\n现在有一个用户上传的报文，发到哪个服务器上，哪个服务器就会断连大概 3-5 分钟左右。\r\n报文格式就是 JSON 加 base64 ，因为图片涉及用户身份证信息没法发。\r\n服务器端没有错误日志。\r\n抓包的看了下，上面是正常 tcp 分片的报文，下面突然是客户端突然没应答了？但是服务端已经收不了请求了。\r\n请求第一次响应 read ECONNRESET 然后再请求响应啥都是 connect ECONNREFUSED\r\n整崩溃了。\r\n[Imgur]( https://i.imgur.com/uGFTbZN.png)","content_rendered":"前提：公司有两台转发服务器，一台 nginx ，一个 IIS 服务，有一个用户信息图片上传接口，已经稳定运行 2 年。<br />现在有一个用户上传的报文，发到哪个服务器上，哪个服务器就会断连大概 3-5 分钟左右。<br />报文格式就是 JSON 加 base64 ，因为图片涉及用户身份证信息没法发。<br />服务器端没有错误日志。<br />抓包的看了下，上面是正常 tcp 分片的报文，下面突然是客户端突然没应答了？但是服务端已经收不了请求了。<br />请求第一次响应 read ECONNRESET 然后再请求响应啥都是 connect ECONNREFUSED<br />整崩溃了。<br />[Imgur]( <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/uGFTbZN.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uGFTbZN.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>)","last_modified":1689553759,"replies":15,"id":957240},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1685063629","name":"career","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1685063629","title":"职场话题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","topics":14560,"footer":"","header":"这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。","title_alternative":"Career","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1685063629","stars":2741,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":770,"parent_node_name":"work"},"member":{"id":469942,"username":"revalue","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/revalue","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dfe5/4070/469942_mini.png?m=1647671000","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dfe5/4070/469942_normal.png?m=1647671000","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dfe5/4070/469942_large.png?m=1647671000","created":1582022180,"last_modified":1647671000},"last_reply_by":"revalue","last_touched":1689566586,"title":"工业互联网是不是一种噱头","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/957327","created":1689562942,"deleted":0,"content":"或者是一种最终普及率不高的东西？ 95%的工厂都用不到","content_rendered":"<p>或者是一种最终普及率不高的东西？ 95%的工厂都用不到</p>\n","last_modified":1689562942,"replies":14,"id":957327},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1689070442","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1689070442","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":57351,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1689070442","stars":8482,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":628679,"username":"LandCruiser","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/LandCruiser","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c2b01e216c511f784611f5cd4525cd1e?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c2b01e216c511f784611f5cd4525cd1e?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c2b01e216c511f784611f5cd4525cd1e?s=73&d=retro","created":1683883536,"last_modified":1683883536},"last_reply_by":"ETCartman","last_touched":1689568794,"title":"如果我选专业的时候知道张雪峰，我也许就不会在志愿栏填一个化工。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/957346","created":1689565316,"deleted":0,"content":"我觉得张雪峰说的很对，优先专业，而不是优先学校，上个二本计算机也好啊。\r\n\r\n我因为选错专业消沉了一段时间\r\n\r\n我们学校也没有转专业的途径，只能找关系走后门转专业，多方托人找到学校党委书记，开口就要十万，放弃了。\r\n\r\n虽然后面我通过自学，毕业之后还是入了行顺利找到工作，但是专业问题对我影响巨大，找工作会被问就不说了。\r\n\r\n我最近想去加拿大读 cs 相关的硕士，依然被专业限制，非相关专业无法申请，这真是个巨大的打击。\r\n\r\n如果当初我知道张雪峰，我的人生会不会顺利一点呢？","content_rendered":"<p>我觉得张雪峰说的很对，优先专业，而不是优先学校，上个二本计算机也好啊。</p>\n<p>我因为选错专业消沉了一段时间</p>\n<p>我们学校也没有转专业的途径，只能找关系走后门转专业，多方托人找到学校党委书记，开口就要十万，放弃了。</p>\n<p>虽然后面我通过自学，毕业之后还是入了行顺利找到工作，但是专业问题对我影响巨大，找工作会被问就不说了。</p>\n<p>我最近想去加拿大读 cs 相关的硕士，依然被专业限制，非相关专业无法申请，这真是个巨大的打击。</p>\n<p>如果当初我知道张雪峰，我的人生会不会顺利一点呢？</p>\n","last_modified":1689565316,"replies":13,"id":957346},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":207105,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3877,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":463871,"username":"yuhaijiang2019","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuhaijiang2019","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a05f/13cf/463871_mini.png?m=1669616750","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a05f/13cf/463871_normal.png?m=1669616750","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a05f/13cf/463871_large.png?m=1669616750","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a05f/13cf/463871_xlarge.png?m=1669616750","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a05f/13cf/463871_xlarge.png?m=1669616750","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a05f/13cf/463871_xlarge.png?m=1669616750","created":1578473156,"last_modified":1669616750},"last_reply_by":"yuhaijiang2019","last_touched":1689568846,"title":"关于相亲软件再后续","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/957356","created":1689567171,"dele